{"tid":912827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自由黨撤回23條議案","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T03:37:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7fd5e772406a2062d2b0b44616a02ba67c0d66","tid":912827,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552638&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=92048f76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552638&h=d88ae742\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552638</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月23日 <br />\n<br />\n自由黨撤回23條議案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181123/large/23la8p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181123%2Flarge%2F23la8p4.jpg&h=f73de878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自由黨早前宣佈將原本由該黨黨魁鍾國斌（圖）提出，有關討論《基本法》23條立法的無約束力議員議案，改為討論中美貿易戰後，不過立會主席梁君彥表明不能改動題目，若鍾不想提出可自行撤回。立法會秘書處昨通知議員，指鍾國斌已正式撤回《基本法》23條立法的上述議案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主黨：對官員當頭棒喝<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉對鍾做法表示歡迎，認為在中美貿易戰下，政府和議員應盡量避免令香港成為中美貿易戰磨心，同時避免採取「寧左勿右」和強硬姿態挑動國際社會。胡又相信，鍾今次決定考慮到美國會一旦接納美中經濟與安全審查委員會報告建議，取消香港獨立關稅區地位，香港在經貿上將受到嚴重影響，「希望啲愛護香港嘅官員同建制派人士，都要聽到同睇到呢個（報告）當頭棒喝」。<br />\n<br />\n美國會委任的美中經濟與安全審查委員會（US-China Economic and Security Review Commission），早前提交2018年度報告，基於北京嚴重侵蝕香港自治以及言論自由，國會應要求美國商務部，重新評估美國科技出口政策，和是否應繼續將香港與大陸，視為兩個獨立關稅區處理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n查許智峯　立會再蒐證<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：保留瞽師杜煥40年前遺音　榮鴻曾復刻南音絕響"},{"pid":"153fe8f7544a208c5f7266602593d77a4b583c02","tid":912827,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"鍾國斌係叛國賊"},{"pid":"9664cc093c7ea78b049017771d26e1928c4f55d1","tid":912827,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"怕死嘅中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620d88000f995c86122d9733b1fc7be8615b9160","tid":912827,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"反中亂港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a718d02fdec95a8f9939ee2c486d71eea56d62","tid":912827,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"真焦土應該再提出23條議案<br />\n睇下呢班契弟到時有咩講"},{"pid":"bba816063f5c919ec7a1879d5f527b232a377bbd","tid":912827,"uid":179908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"渣㗎自由黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}